<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-GB">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Offline decision log, {{SESSION_DATE}}</title>
<style>
  :root {
    color-scheme: light;
  }
  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    background: #f6f7f9;
    color: #1c2128;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .sheet {
    max-width: 56rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #e2e5ea;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  header {
    padding: 2rem 2.25rem 1.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e5ea;
    background: #fbfbfd;
  }
  header h1 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .session-date {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    color: #5b6470;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .north-star {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    background: #eef4ff;
    border: 1px solid #d3e0fb;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .north-star .label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: #3a5cab;
  }
  .north-star .value {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .body {
    padding: 1.75rem 2.25rem 2.25rem;
  }
  .body h2 {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2c3540;
  }
  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  thead th {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 0.65rem 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: #5b6470;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e5ea;
  }
  tbody td {
    padding: 0.8rem 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eef0f3;
    vertical-align: top;
  }
  tbody tr:last-child td {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .col-timestamp {
    white-space: nowrap;
    color: #5b6470;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    width: 12rem;
  }
  .col-event {
    white-space: nowrap;
    font-weight: 600;
    width: 14rem;
  }
  .col-detail {
    color: #2c3540;
  }
  .empty {
    padding: 1.5rem 0.75rem;
    color: #5b6470;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  footer {
    padding: 1.25rem 2.25rem 1.75rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #e2e5ea;
    color: #8a93a0;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="sheet">
    <header>
      <h1>Offline decision log</h1>
      <p class="session-date">Session date: {{SESSION_DATE}}</p>
      <div class="north-star">
        <span class="label">North Star</span>
        <p class="value">{{NORTH_STAR}}</p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="body">
      <h2>Events recorded while offline mode was active</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th class="col-timestamp">Timestamp</th>
            <th class="col-event">Event type</th>
            <th class="col-detail">Detail</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <!-- BEGIN ROWS -->
          <!-- Renderer: replace the single example <tr> below with one <tr> per logged event; do not emit this example row verbatim. -->
          <tr>
            <td class="col-timestamp">{{ROW_TIMESTAMP}}</td>
            <td class="col-event">{{ROW_EVENT_TYPE}}</td>
            <td class="col-detail">{{ROW_DETAIL}}</td>
          </tr>
          <!-- END ROWS -->
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <footer>
      Produced by playbook offline mode. Events are limited to those that occurred because you were absent: forced-without-you decisions made after the wait window elapsed, external-manager consultations, waits, and notification sends.
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
